title: Rolex Paris Masters: Zizou Bergs vs Jannik Sinner

title: Will Trump announce TikTok deal by Thursday?
description:
This market will resolve to “Yes” if Donald Trump officially announces that a deal for the sale or restructuring of TikTok’s U.S. operations has been finalized by Thursday, October 30, 2025, 11:59 PM ET. Otherwise, this market will resolve to “No”.
